# Project: Richard Pillaca — Portfolio Website v2
# Next.js portfolio → Deploy on Vercel → richardpillaca.com
# Blueprint: @docs/PRD.md | Progress: @docs/progress.txt

## What We're Building
Personal portfolio for Richard Pillaca Burga — Data Analyst & BI Developer.
Design language: Michelle Liu (clean/minimal) + Vipul Soni (case study depth) + Noah Barbaros (essays).
Reference: @docs/ARCHITECTURE.md for full site map and component breakdown.

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 16, App Router, TypeScript strict mode
- Styling: Tailwind CSS utility classes only (no inline styles)
- Deployment: Vercel (push to GitHub → auto-deploy)
- Content: MDX for essays/blog posts
- No database — static content from data files in `src/data/`

## Project Scripts
- `pnpm dev` — Dev server on port 3000
- `pnpm build` — Production build (must pass before any PR)
- `pnpm lint` — ESLint (zero errors required)
- `npx tsc --noEmit` — Type check only

## Site Structure (App Router)
```
src/app/
├── page.tsx              — Home (/)
├── projects/
│   ├── page.tsx          — Project gallery (/projects)
│   └── [slug]/page.tsx   — Individual case study (/projects/[slug])
├── essays/
│   ├── page.tsx          — Essays list (/essays)
│   └── [slug]/page.tsx   — Individual essay (/essays/[slug])
├── about/page.tsx        — About (/about)
└── layout.tsx            — Root layout (Nav + Footer)

src/components/           — Reusable UI components
src/data/                 — Project content, essay metadata (TypeScript objects)
src/lib/                  — Utilities, MDX helpers
public/                   — Images, fonts, static assets
```

